Package temp.fibHeap.stixar.graph.check

Graph property checkers.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
DigraphChecker Interface for a property checker of digraphs.
UGraphChecker Interface for a property checker of undirected graphs.
 

Class Summary
AcyclicChecker Checks whether or not a digraph is acyclic.
AntiSymmetricChecker Check whether a digraph has no edges (u,v) such that there exists an edge (v,u).
BipartiteChecker Checks whether or not an undirected graph is bipartite.
ForestChecker Check whether or not a digraph is a forest.
LoopFreeChecker Check a graph for loops.
MultiEdgeFreeChecker Check whether or not a graph has multiple edges.
SymmetricChecker Checks if a graph is symmetric.
TreeChecker Check whether or not a digraph is a tree.
UForestChecker Checks whether or not an undirected graph is a forest.
UTreeChecker Checks whether or not an undirected graph is a tree.
 

Enum Summary
BipartiteChecker.EdgeStatus  
BipartiteChecker.Partition partition names in a bipartite graph.
DigraphProperty A set of properties which may or may not hold for a given digraph.
UForestChecker.EdgeStat  
UGraphProperty A set of properties which may or may not hold for a given undirected graph.
